{ "title": "Apartment 3 Room - EUR 292,000", "description": "Modern, designer-furnished apartment located on the 10th storey of the EUROPALACE building, featuring views of the beautiful Little Fatra, Martinky, Dubeň, including Vlčince and the surrounding area thanks to its elevated position. LAYOUT: This type of apartment layout is located only up to the 10th storey, making it the highest positioned and sufficiently illuminated, with orientation towards three cardinal directions (east, southeast, and north) . It has a completely ideal orientation compared to other (west-facing) apartments, as in the summer the apartment does not overheat and it is comfortable to live in without the need for air conditioning (which is good for both your health and your wallet considering the costs) . The apartment is sensibly divided into a living (social) area and a space designated for relaxation or study. The total associated area is 94.93 m2, which consists of : entrance hallway / 6.82 m2 / with a built-in wardrobe measuring 3 meters, making storage in the apartment hassle-free, southeast-facing living room with kitchen / up to 25.56 m2 /, offering views of the Little Fatra and Martinky, providing beautiful vistas of the Žilina basin mountains. The living room is connected to the kitchen, which has a built-in refrigerator, microwave oven, dishwasher, induction hob, BOSCH dishwasher, oven, Electrolux microwave, carbon extractor hood from the FRANKE brand, and a spacious brick shower enclosure with storage ledge, a bespoke kitchen unit with built-in appliances (induction hob, BOSCH dishwasher) and (oven, Electrolux microwave), a carbon extractor hood from the FRANK brand, a sliding kitchen table with designer base that can serve as a workspace while cooking, as well as a dining table during dinner. Silgranit sink by BLANCO and faucet with a pull-out spray of the same brand and shade. All the lights in the apartment are LED, the hallway features designer fixtures that tastefully complement the apartment's aesthetics, and the rooms are equipped with lights that allow for changing the white light color (warm / neutral / cool) as well as brightness adjustment, including dimming. The living room with kitchen features a total of 7 lighting options, allowing you to choose the right setting according to your mood and type of activity (while cooking, you will definitely appreciate plenty of light, but preferences change when watching TV or having guests) and additionally comes with a practical single remote control for all. The rooms are equipped with radiators with thermostatic valves, and the bathroom features a towel radiator, all of which can be controlled centrally using a digital thermostat. The higher standard of Europalace offers very high-quality wood - aluminum windows, which not only provide thermal insulation but also effectively soundproof the apartment from the outside environment. LOCATION: The address of your home would be the sought-after multifunctional complex EUROPALACE, located on the edge of the popular district of Žilina - Vlčince. The high quality, comfort, and safety of living are enhanced by nearby sports and relaxation facilities, as well as a variety of commercial and dining establishments in the area. The location also offers excellent access to the city center and to the expressway connections. The property is located in a highly sought-after area, offering complete civic amenities and many additional benefits. The Europalace complex itself offers premium services : the entire property is monitored 24 hours a day by a security service (SBS), with camera surveillance and monitoring of common areas, underground parking, and more. The building itself houses a restaurant, a dental clinic, a client center of the Ministry of Interior of the Slovak Republic, as well as the headquarters of our real estate agency MGM. It is just a few minutes' walk to grocery stores (Kaufland, LIDL), Dubeň shopping center, restaurants, primary and nursery schools, fitness facilities, ŽILPO polyclinic, and the University of Žilina. Tennis courts, an indoor swimming pool, a summer swimming pool, an athletic complex, and the Chrasť forest park sports and recreation zone are just a short distance away. The city center of Žilina is within a 5-minute drive, or a 15-minute walk. Direct access to the expressway connecting the routes Bratislava - Košice - Čadca is available within 3 minutes. public transport stops are located 50 m from the main entrance of the building. The price of the property is 292,000 € . Monthly management fees for the apartment: 215 € / month including security services. Parking: private parking space in the underground garage is not included in the price. The price of the premium parking space, where you can park not only a car but also a trailer and a motorcycle, is available for an additional fee (the owner is currently preparing for an electric charging station) ."}
